=== 執政理念 ===
不丹政府於2008年11月正式启用一个[[國民幸福總值|國民幸福總值]]的指数，以对应世界通用的[[国内生产总值|国内生产总值]]。国王秉承其父早在1970年代就提出的理念，认为國民幸福總值比国内生产总值更重要，经过数十年的规划，终于在近几年成功制定了一套相当繁复的“幸福指标”，施行于全国。
=== 海外人氣 ===
2013年，數次獲得邀請出訪印度<ref>{{cite web|title=Republic Day: Bhutan King chief guest at 26th Jan parade|work=The Economic Times|date=2013-01-26|url=http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2013-01-26/news/36564065_1_jigme-khesar-namgyel-wangchuck-republic-day-celebrations-chief-guest|accessdate=2014-11-02|language=en|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305074537/http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2013-01-26/news/36564065_1_jigme-khesar-namgyel-wangchuck-republic-day-celebrations-chief-guest|dead-url=no}}</ref>，另外也出席[[李光耀|李光耀]]的葬禮<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/bhutan-queens-facebook-post-on-national-flag-at-half-mast-on-sunday-to-mark-mr-lee-kuan|agency=The Straits Times|date=2015-03-30|title=Bhutan Queen's Facebook post on national flag at half-mast on Sunday to mark Mr Lee Kuan Yew's funeral|accessdate=2019-10-18|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820193025/http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/bhutan-queens-facebook-post-on-national-flag-at-half-mast-on-sunday-to-mark-mr-lee-kuan|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

